ng far better than begging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Zubayr ibn al-\u2018Awwam reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFor one of you to take his rope and carry a bundle of wood to sell, by which Allah preserves his dignity, is better than begging from people who may give or withhold.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1471\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41150,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/08\/zubayr-secret\/","url_meta":{"origin":7912,"position":1},"title":"Zubayr on Sincerity: Keep some of your good deeds private","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qays reported: Al-Zubayr ibn al-\u2018Awwam, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever among you can keep some of his good deeds hidden, let him do so.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34751 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0632\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u064f\u0651\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":""